What is a Frequency Polygon?
========================================================
```{r fig.width=8, fig.height=3, out.height=400, fig.align="center", echo=FALSE}
freqpolygon( ~age, data=HELPrct, lwd=3, par.settings=col.whitebg(), 
             panel=function(x,...) { 
  panel.xhistogram(x,...);
  panel.freqpolygon(x,...)}
             )
```

